# ShadCN / Radix — UI SSOT

**SSOT:** `packages/ui/src/components/ui/*` (ShadCN + Radix). Add primitives via:

```bash
cd packages/ui && npx shadcn@latest add <component> -y
```

## Required

- Buttons → `Button` / `ButtonLink` / `buttonVariants` from `@ludecker/ui`
- Menus, dialogs, popovers → ShadCN Radix components from `@ludecker/ui`
- Styling utilities → `cn()` from `@ludecker/ui`
- Tailwind entry → `apps/website/src/styles/shadcn.css`; theme tokens → `@ludecker/ui/shadcn-theme.css`

## Forbidden

- Custom `ui-button` / `buttonClassName` / hand-rolled dropdowns
- Duplicate ShadCN copies under `apps/website/components/ui`
- Raw `<button>` for UI chrome (admin, docs header, toolbars) — use `Button`
- Base UI (`@base-ui/react`) — Radix only

## Layout CSS

Docs/public layout chrome may keep token CSS (`docs-*.css`) for structure; interactive controls inside it must still use ShadCN `Button` and Radix primitives.
